Package: labelprinter-vc500w
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}
Recommends: python3-argcomplete, python3-pil
Description: command-line driver for Brother VC-500W label printers
 Control Brother VC-500W color label printers over TCP/IP from Debian.
 .
 This package installs the Python module together with the bclprinter
 command-line interface for checking printer status, releasing stale
 locks, and printing JPEG labels.
